"2020-01-06T21:47:14.000Z","msg":"咁便衣扮示威者捉鬼又點算"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:54:35.000Z","msg":"係喎<br />\n狗扮人捉鬼點拆？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T22:13:37.000Z","msg":"言語上了解下咩事先，勸佢唔好理人裝修<br />\n以防一黎就出手一陣又打撚錯手足<br />\n<br />\n其實大家既心態接受到暴力就冇問題<br />\n有人大嗌捉人食煙會唔會有人一窩蜂衝上去圍個煙剷？<br />\n大家心態當裝修火魔獅鳥係食煙咁，家常便飯，自然唔會去捉<br />\n<br />\n心態唔易改變，希望大家日後諗到個口號or字眼類似不割之類，係種心理暗示，令人想割都逼自己接受"},{"pid":"fd427a34df636569963922d05c70f245432e27b2","tid":1814181,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T22:14:07.000Z","msg":"捉鬼根本同左膠一樣<br />\n都係阻撚住哂"},{"pid":"49816bcf13d386e64266a1175c0eb37063c059f0","tid":1814181,"uid":237237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b66ba9d6d0d1773b0f628519d1d2ebb4efc8add1","tid":1814181,"uid":44071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ca76c1a6e2ee33392ceaa410ee13d6e75def432","tid":1814181,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:47:14.000Z","msg":"咁便衣扮示威者捉鬼又點算"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:54:35.000Z","msg":"係喎<br />\n狗扮人捉鬼點拆？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T22:15:25.000Z","msg":"捉鬼=阻膠"},{"pid":"2bcb540971b11a8ea943c284e66a4b729d6f6717","tid":1814181,"uid":112502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6891f26998e52f28a82fb0fdecb28172710bc99","tid":1814181,"uid":289593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bba3a0b8495404acde3532a6fc642e5e0ff2985","tid":1814181,"uid":112502,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d8cbc274fa91d25980aaa59446feec6de38ea6b","tid":1814181,"uid":71193,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:14:12.000Z","msg":"Agger<br />\n要強調暴力/武力既正當性<br />\n係官逼民反"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:19:58.000Z","msg":"明明早期遊行都一定出現暴力埸面<br />\n唔明點解經歷咁多野之後反而倒退，依一刻先變返和理非時段<br />\n黑警想幫手裝修玩火魔絕對要支持<br />\n無理由勇武左半年，依家先潔癖上身想拎返個和平獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:58:22.000Z","msg":"突然loop返一開頭捉鬼風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T22:23:41.000Z","msg":"諗到既係<br />\n一黎真係有鬼但大家唔識應對，永遠想破壞鬼既行動，但鬼既目標唔係佢地有咩動作，目標得一個就係搞撚亂大家<br />\n二黎理大加區選之後，大家偏向玩和理非路線，玩到d潔癖出返晒黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw冇勇武令黑警出醜態，警民對立會冷卻，catch唔到人眼球即野冇新聞會報，國際回響只會愈黎愈細，係呀好撚和平呀，不過和平玩法之下人民絕對唔夠中共玩，因爲規矩係中共定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f388dc48e6500f5e597d6b5e0f98f1299638f6","tid":1814181,"uid":112502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49816bcf13d386e64266a1175c0eb37063c059f0","tid":1814181,"uid":237237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b66ba9d6d0d1773b0f628519d1d2ebb4efc8add1","tid":1814181,"uid":44071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ca76c1a6e2ee33392ceaa410ee13d6e75def432","tid":1814181,"uid":27416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:47:14.000Z","msg":"咁便衣扮示威者捉鬼又點算"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T21:54:35.000Z","msg":"係喎<br />\n狗扮人捉鬼點拆？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T22:15:25.000Z","msg":"捉鬼=阻膠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T22:33:48.000Z","msg":"阻人獅鳥既以前點應對<br />\n咪咁對返d捉鬼撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就唔希望一開波打撚柒佢<br />\n好易打錯未清醒既手足<br />\n至少拉開佢對質下先"},{"pid":"7f7117af781ec80b21266c3f3c36d13063aa773d","tid":1814181,"uid":112502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T22:37:38.000Z","msg":"重點都係大家要有個信念<br />\n允許任何暴力，只要唔係傷緊自己人"},{"pid":"6bbeb32b80b220e89390257e53063afd8f80c8fb","tid":1814181,"uid":112502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T22:43:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉鬼死全家</span></span>"},{"pid":"076216f6c9527aa10aa24e5a5c4266bd007e6cdc","tid":1814181,"uid":118312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T22:45:02.000Z","msg":"冇計<br />\n成個亞洲教育問題<br />\n教撚到香港人太撚斯文同守規矩<br />\n見住3/4個便衣捉1/2個手足<br />\n個個淨係識攞手機出來影<br />\n<br />\n係呀係呀要影低不公義俾人睇呀<br />\n當叫救命都冇人救嘅時候<br />\n仲有邊個敢做勇武"},{"pid":"8c7bc4365db28ed8acd1e47acdfee2983ce61aee","tid":1814181,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T23:12:52.000Z","msg":"我地唔需要教條主義,兄弟爬山,各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979b15278784b3794a368adb6b0e028b389faa2b","tid":1814181,"uid":223256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f7117af781ec80b21266c3f3c36d13063aa773d","tid":1814181,"uid":112502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T22:37:38.000Z","msg":"重點都係大家要有個信念<br />\n允許任何暴力，只要唔係傷緊自己人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T23:25:40.000Z","msg":"錯<br />\nteam kill 都唔割"},{"pid":"c434afe42d6febd8e391a15d749a2c8861681cd7","tid":1814181,"uid":112502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:10:58.000Z","msg":"推"}]}